== Run the catalyst manually ==
{{Note|Please read this section if you want to make stages manually.}}
Catalyst contained in main tree does not support Gentoo/FreeBSD. Details please see {{Bug|363577}}. Please use it on gentoo-bsd overlay.

https://gitweb.gentoo.org/proj/gentoo-bsd.git/tree/dev-util/catalyst

Sample spec are available from gentoo-bsd overlay. Please use after replace the contents.

https://gitweb.gentoo.org/proj/gentoo-bsd.git/tree/scripts/mkstages/specs/

{{RootCmd|catalyst -C target{{=}}snapshot version_stamp{{=}}20150712
|catalyst -f stage1_tmp.spec
|catalyst -f stage2_tmp.spec
|catalyst -f stage3_tmp.spec
|catalyst -f stage1.spec
|catalyst -f stage2.spec
|catalyst -f stage3.spec}}
